==English==

===Etymology===
[[Portmanteau word]] of '''[[gigantic]]''' and '''[[enormous]]'''.

===Pronunciation===
*Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ɔː(r)məs|-ɔː(r)məs]]

===Adjective===
{{en-adj-more}}

# Very [[big]].
#:''He drove up in a '''ginormous''' [[stretch limo]].''
#:''That [[book]] was '''ginormous'''!''


